    <string name="about_text_description_title">Game Description</string>
    <string name="about_text_detailed_description">
        The Wiki Game is inspired by the well known "Wiki Challenge",
        where you get to both play and enrich your knowledge on the Wikipedia platform.
        The gameplay idea is an association game that gives you a starting article,
        and through the available links scattered across the article you are on, you can navigate to other articles.
        The goal is to reach end article you designated with the helps and setbacks you decide on.
        Challenge yourself and your friends and learn something new everyday!
    </string>
